items.name: KURIO XTREME NEXT
items.shortDescription: Kurio Next is the ultimate Android tablet built especially for children. Featuring the latest tablet technology, packed with kid-friendly apps & games, with best-in-class parental controls built in, this kid tablet is ready to go right out of the box. Best of all, parents can let their kids surf the web with complete peace of mind. Kurio Next includes a free lifetime subscription to Kurio’s proprietary Kurio Genius internet filtering system, covering more than 18 billion websites in 200 languages, plus in-app web filtering! Kurio Next allows parents to customize their child’s tablet experience in a password-protected Parental Area for up to eight child profiles. Parents have complete control to set time limits on each child’s use, manage which apps are allowed in each child’s profile, and even create a list of specific approved & blocked sites or categories when browsing the web. Kids will have lots of fun with all the preloaded apps, games and educational content, including top gaming apps like Subway Surfers and Berry Rush, kid-safe videos from YouTube Kids, and new apps that teach valuable STEM skills as they play. Plus, get new content free for an entire year! Kurio’s Surprise-A-Week App program delivers new apps, games or e-books directly to your device for you and your child to discover, every week, for 52 weeks. Access millions more apps through the Google Play store! Kurio Next comes with a shockproof and spillproof bumper, so you can take it with you anywhere. Kurio also offers live 24/7 customer support with tech experts based in the U.S. to resolve any issues, so kids can get back to their tablet and parents can look like tech support superheroes. Within the 9.7" LED, 2048 x 1536 pixels render text and images with extreme sharpness. items.name: Lenovo Yoga Tab 3 Plus Tablet
items.shortDescription: Say goodbye to your TV. If you love movies and TV, the Yoga Tab 3 Plus is for you. At 1.40 lbs (637 g), with four usage modes, this splashproof tablet will elevate your viewing experience to new immersive levels of comfort. And with a pristine 10.1” Quad High Definition (QHD) display, theater-caliber JBL speakers, and marathon battery life, you can enjoy the show absolutely anywhere.
items.longDescription: <ul><li>Four Modes For Comfortable Watching Scroll through recipes while you cook, check your social feeds while you eat, and watch movies while you work out. The Yoga Tab 3 Plus is designed to fit your lifestyle and its innovative design gives you multiple ways to use it. Stand it up, hold it, tilt it, or hang it.</li><li>Your Personal TV The Yoga Tab 3 Plus is the perfect companion for movie and TV lovers alike. It offers a pristine display, long lasting battery life, and theater-caliber JBL speakers, perfect for watching video on demand. And because of its ultra portability, you can carry it with you and experience on-the-go entertainment, when you want it, where you want it, and with no fighting over the remote control.</li><li>Color Enhanced Technology With in-built Technicolor Color Enhance technology, the Yoga Tab 3 Plus is perfect for immersive gaming and rich, detailed video. It boasts a wide angle, 10.1" Quad High Definition (QHD), In-Plane Switching (IPS) display, delivering crisp, bright visuals for a better viewing experience under all angles and ambient lights.</li><li>Sharing is Caring Share your favorite movies or youtube videos with friends using Lenovo Media Cast. Wirelessly cast your phone’s screen to the Yoga Tab 3 Plus when you need a bigger screen. Or you can leverage its powerful speakers via bluetooth to play music from phones and laptops for the ultimate sound experience.</li><li>Immersive Cinematic Moving Audio The Yoga Tab 3 Plus delivers rich theater sound that you’ll rarely experience on any other tablet. The four integrated front-facing JBL speakers and powerfully immersive Dolby Atmos provide loud, clear, and dynamic moving audio that flows all around you, putting you at the centre of the action–even without headphones!</li><li>Marathon Battery Life With its outstanding battery life the Yoga Tab 3 Plus just keeps going and going. With up to 18 hours on one charge, it’s enough to watch two seasons of your favorite TV show back to back. The battery is so powerful, it can be used as a USB 'On-the-Go' powerbank, allowing you to charge all of your other devices. In addition, its in-box 24W fast charger ensures you’ll never run out of juice.</li><li>Stylish and Splashproof When it comes to style, the Yoga Tab 3 Plus steals the show. It comes in puma black with a textured, leather-like finish, durable metal chassis, and kickstand. But its durability isn’t only limited to the quality of its materials–the Tab 3 is also splashproof so you can use it anywhere without fear of getting it wet.</li><li>Integrated Camera Rear: 13MP Front: 5MP</li><li>Audio 4-JBL-speaker soundbar with Dolby Atmos technology</li><li>Storage Up to 32GB</li><li>Battery 3 Cell Lithium-Ion</li><li>Display 10.1" QHD (2560 x 1600) LCD IPS Multi-Touch</li><li>Connectors USB 2.0 Type-C 3.5 mm Audio Jack MicroSD Card Slot Micro SIM card slot (LTE SKU only)</li><li>WiFi and Bluetooth 11a/b/g/n/ac Wi-Fi wireless + Bluetooth 4.0</li></ul>

items.shortDescription: The Apple iPad mini with WiFi gives you the power and functionality of the iPad in a slightly smaller, more portable size. A 7.9-inch LED-backlit screen clearly displays your apps, videos and websites on this small, hand-held device. Powered by the A5 chip and running iOS 5, this tablet allows you to efficiently use whatever apps you may choose from the over 200,000 available on the App Store. The white iPad mini also has built-in WiFi capability and is compatible with 802.11a/b/g/n networks so you can use it at home or with open networks wherever you go. A FaceTime camera and iSight camera allow you to use this device for video chatting with family and friends and also to take pictures or record video. You can use the Apple iPad mini for up to 10 hours on a single battery charge.
items.longDescription: <br><b>Apple iPad mini with WiFi 7.9" Touchscreen Tablet PC, Refurbished:</b><br><br><b>Technical Specifications:</b><ul><li>A5X Dual-Core processor</li><li>7.9" touchscreen</li><li>Built-in 802.11a/b/g/n WiFi and AT&T 4G + LTE</li></ul><b>Additional Features:</b><ul><li>5MP webcam and FaceTime webcam</li><li>Apple Lightning connector, headphone port</li><li>64GB onboard storage memory</li><li>Up to 10 hours of run time on a full charge</li></ul><b>Software and Applications:</b><ul><li>iOS 5 OS</li><li>App Store</li><li>Media Formats: Popular media formats</li></ul><b>What's in the Box:</b><ul><li>Tablet, battery and AC adapter</li></ul><br><b>What's a Tablet PC?</b><br><br>Tablet PCs are compact, ultra-portable entertainment devices that let you read email, surf the Internet, read eBooks, view photos, play games, listen to music and watch video files. Most tablets are based on a smaller operating system, which allows you to purchase and download additional applications from supported stores. Tablet PCs do not have a CD/DVD drive and will not run Microsoft Windows or its applications. Tablet PCs function as a secondary device for casual entertainment purposes, and are not meant to replace a computer. They are ideal for use around the home and on the go with WiFi or 3-4G mobile broadband connections (pay as you go, contract may be required for service).
